definitions.definition: A town and civil parish with a town council on the northeast coast of the Isle of Wight , England .
A suburb and local government area (the City of Ryde ) in Sydney , New South Wales , Australia , named after Ryde, IoW.
An unincorporated community in Sacramento County , California , United States , named after Ryde, IoW.
